data.description: *Buyer terminated due to an emergency* East facing charming 2 story home with an incredible open floorplan sits on an over-sized corner lot. The home offers 4 very spacious & comfortable bedrooms located on the second level, there are 3 living areas in the home, a versatile formal living & dining area, a huge family room with an inviting wood burning fireplace that flows seamlessly into the kitchen creating a spacious open area perfect for hosting friends & family. The second level living area is perfect for a game or media room. The private owners retreat gives you plenty of room to spread out & enjoy some privacy. The generous backyard has a substantial amount of space to create your very own backyard oasis.
